ked husband\" who willingly submits to his wife's control...</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"110083","season":1,"vote_average":10,"vote_count":1},"modified":"2024-12-25T14:32:07.000Z","cast":["Liu Wai-Hung","Jaclyn Chu Wai-San","Lâm Bảo Di","Cutie Mui Siu-Wai","Noel Leung","Trần Quốc Bang","Trần Gia Huy","Jimmy Wong Shu-Kei","Chan On-ying","Lý Long Cơ","Nam Hung","Law Ho-Kai","Ngải Uy","Wong San","Vương Duy Đức"],"director":["Mai Tiểu Thanh"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Liu Wai-Hung","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Liu Wai-Hung","tmdb_id":998678,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ardsrPTdd2qQsm0tW5WqEDu0hNl.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/998678"},{"name":"Jaclyn Chu Wai-San","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Jaclyn Chu Wai-San","tmdb_id":1137012,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aXs0R12ZCEwvAThaZlP7Jj1yex1.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1137012"},{"name":"Lâm Bảo Di","name_vi":"Lâm Bảo Di","name_original":"Bowie Lam Bo-Yee","tmdb_id":552084,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7scIX24RyIlibdyeXljnEPjXeKO.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/552084"},{"name":"Cutie Mui Siu-Wai","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Cutie Mui Siu-Wai","tmdb_id":1407468,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/h4DDhRthWnp6KwbZcmG2MUL1W6F.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1407468"},{"name":"Noel Leung","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Noel Leung","tmdb_id":140483,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zfZvegM9Jzagw1sRGJ4mhNarQ1i.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/140483"},{"name":"Trần Quốc Bang","name_vi":"Trần Quốc Bang","name_original":"Power Chan Kwok-Pong","tmdb_id":66010,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/o5wZEj3oS527cE4g1JdfVledphb.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/66010"},{"name":"Trần Gia Huy","name_vi":"Trần Gia Huy","name_original":"Gary Chan Ga-Fai","tmdb_id":1624824,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r2ocfvzwvBZBrYMmF6uOqDRwvd7.jpg","tmdb_url"